data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Nestled in the charming, active resort golf community of Beacon Woods in Hudson, Florida, this home boasts a delightful blend of modern comforts and classic charm. Offering a serene and inviting atmosphere, this residence provides an ideal haven for spacious living. Step inside to a formal foyer and discover the expansive floor plan featuring a living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, and family room. Natural light cascades through large windows, illuminating the space. The U-shaped kitchen offers a pass-through to the family room and ample counterspace for the culinary enthusiast. Three bedrooms and two bathrooms are thoughtfully displayed in a split plan. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with a step-in shower. This residence presents an exceptional opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort and convenience, providing the tranquility of a residential area while conveniently close to local amenities, parks, schools, and major thoroughfares. The well-maintained exterior boasts an inviting front porch and a huge rear lanai with brick pavers. Enjoy Florida living from the screened lanai, perfect for relaxing, entertaining, and savoring the Florida weather. Additional features include an inside laundry room and an oversized 2-car garage with an updated eco-smart water heater, garage door opener, and irrigation system. The roof was replaced in 2011. Come and see all that this delightful home has to offer and make it your own. Seller offering up to $500 Home warranty for the buyer. Make an offer today.
